title: Pictures of the week: Aug. 25-31, 2015
content:
A roundup of the best of the Bay Area News Group s photojournalism from Aug. 25 to Aug. 31, 2015. 
  
CLICK ON THE PHOTO ABOVE TO SEE THE SLIDE SHOW. Giants Madison Bumgarner delivers a pitch against the Chicago Cubs at AT&T Park on Thursday, Aug. 27, 2015, in San Francisco, Calif. The Giants beat the Cubs 9-1. (John Green/Bay Area News Group)
